# Puchi Backend

Monorepo Go microservices với **Kratos v3**. Service modules trong `app/`, workspace qua `go.work`.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Ngôn ngữ | Go 1.26 |
| Framework | Kratos v3 (HTTP/gRPC hybrid, Protobuf-first) |
| DI | Wire (compile-time) |
| Auth | Auth-service (Limen) — `app/auth/` opaque session + Bearer |
| Auth middleware | `pkg/auth/` — session introspect via `GET /internal/session` |
| Database | PostgreSQL 18 (CloudNativePG), schema `auth.*` + `core.*` |
| Cache | Valkey/Redis |
| Message Queue | NATS (event-driven, outbox pattern) |
| Object Storage | Cloudflare R2 (S3 API) + CDN `cdn.puchi.io.vn` |
| Email | Tino SMTP via notification (`email.send`) |
| Migration | goose |

## Cấu trúc monorepo

```
puchi-backend/
├── app/                           # Go service modules
│   ├── auth/                      # Limen auth-service — identity, OAuth, sessions
│   ├── core/                      # Profile, onboarding, social, game, stats
│   ├── learn/                     # Learning content & progress
│   ├── media/                     # Upload (R2)
│   └── notification/              # Prefs, Gotify push, email.send → Tino SMTP
├── pkg/                           # Shared Kit library
│   ├── auth/                      # Bearer session introspect middleware
│   ├── nats/                      # Subject constants + ConnectOptional
│   └── apierr/                    # HTTP JSON error envelope + gRPC helpers
├── go.work                        # Go workspace (dev only)
└── Makefile                       # Build helper
```

## Quy tắc layered architecture (Kratos)

```
internal/
├── service/       # Transport layer — proto server impl, validate input
├── biz/           # Domain logic — usecases, entities, repo interfaces
└── data/          # Data layer — repository implementations (DB, cache, publisher)
```

**Dependency rule:** `service -> biz -> data` (biz không import data)

## Auth middleware — `pkg/auth/`

Shared package cho **opaque Bearer session introspect**, tất cả backend service (trừ auth) đều import.

| File | Mô tả |
|------|-------|
| `auth.go` | `InitAuth(authServiceURL)` — tạo `SessionValidator` |
| `jwt.go` | `SessionValidator` — `GET /internal/session`, cache ~60s; `JWTValidator` = alias |
| `middleware.go` | Parse `Authorization: Bearer`, inject UserID (+ roles nếu có) vào context |
| `context.go` | `UserIDFromContext()`, `RolesFromContext()`, `HasRole()` |

Session verification flow:
```
Request → Authorization: Bearer <opaque>
       → SessionValidator.ParseAndValidate()
       → GET {auth_service_url}/internal/session (cached ~60s)
       → Extract user id → inject context
```

Không dùng JWT/JWKS.

## Auth-service — `app/auth/`

Thin Limen service (không phải Kratos layered). Xem `auth-service.mdc` rule.

## Docker build pattern

**QUAN TRỌNG:** Mỗi service import `pkg/auth/` → cần `replace` directive trong `go.mod`:
```
require github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/pkg v0.0.0
replace github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/pkg => ../../pkg
```

Dockerfile phải copy `pkg/` vào build context (build từ monorepo root):
```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.26 AS builder
WORKDIR /src
COPY pkg/go.mod pkg/go.sum ./pkg/
COPY app/{service}/go.mod app/{service}/go.sum ./app/{service}/
RUN cd app/{service} && go mod download
COPY pkg/ ./pkg/
COPY app/{service}/ ./app/{service}/
RUN cd app/{service} && go build -o /bin/{service} ./cmd/{service}/
```

CI matrix (`.github/workflows/backend.yml`): `context: .`, `file: app/{service}/Dockerfile`

## CI/CD

- **CI**: GitHub Actions (`backend.yml`) — Matrix build 5 services (auth, core, learn, media, notification), Go 1.26
- **Paths trigger**: `app/**`, `pkg/**`
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-{service}`
- **Ports**: Auth HTTP **8000**; other services HTTP 8000 + gRPC 9000

## Kết nối Infra

| Service | Internal DNS |
|---------|--------------|
| Auth-service | `auth-service.puchi-backend.svc.cluster.local:8000` |
| Auth introspect | `http://auth-service.puchi-backend:8000/internal/session` |
| PostgreSQL (Puchi) | `pg-puchi-rw.puchi-db.svc.cluster.local:5432` |
| NATS | `nats.platform.svc.cluster.local:4222` |
| R2 (media) | `https://<ACCOUNT_ID>.r2.cloudflarestorage.com` (bucket `puchi-media`, CDN `cdn.puchi.io.vn`) |
| Valkey/Redis | `valkey.platform.svc.cluster.local:6379` |

## Dev Local

```bash
# Auth-service (phải chạy trước) — cần LIMEN_SECRET đúng 32 bytes
export LIMEN_SECRET="$(openssl rand -base64 24 | head -c 32)"
# apply app/auth/migrations/001_limen_schema.up.sql
cd app/auth && go run ./cmd/auth/ -conf ../../configs

# Backend service khác
cd app/core && go run ./cmd/core/

# Config: auth.auth_service_url = http://localhost:8000
```
